column2: SELECT m.int_id, m.ra AS ra_card, m.dec AS dec_card, m.z as redshift, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra_sdss, o.dec AS dec_sdss, o.u, o.err_u, o.extinction_u, o.g, o.err_g, o.extinction_g, o.r, o.err_r, o.extinction_r, o.i, o.err_i, o.extinction_i, o.z, o.err_z, o.extinction_z, o.petroMag_u, o.petroMagErr_u, o.petroMag_g, o.petroMagErr_g, o.petroMag_r, o.petroMagErr_r, o.petroMag_i, o.petroMagErr_i, o.petroMag_z, o.petroMagErr_z, o.petroRad_r, o.petroRadErr_r, o.petroR5#_r, o.petroR5#Err_r, o.petroR9#_r, o.petroR9#Err_r, e.Flux_OIII_#, Flux_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_NII_#, e.Flux_NII_#_Err, e.Flux_Ha_#, e.Flux_Ha_#_Err, e.Flux_Hb_#, e.Flux_Hb_#_Err, e.Flux_SII_#, e.Flux_SII_#_Err, e.Flux_SII_#, e.Flux_SII_#_Err, e.Flux_OII_#, e.Flux_OII_#_Err, e.Flux_NeIII_#, e.Flux_NeIII_#_Err, e.Flux_NeV_#, e.Flux_NeV_#_Err, e.ebmv, e.ebmv_err, s.z as redshift, s.class as specClass into mydb.ThePeas_AllParams_#_May FROM MyDB.Peas_enum AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = o.objid LEFT JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON g.specobjid = o.specobjid LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON e.specobjid = s.specobjid
